00:25:40.630 --> 00:25:44.390 align:middle line:84%
>> So this is the
famous Bench of Dreams.

00:25:44.390 --> 00:25:47.190 align:middle line:84%
I know there's
one in Costa Rica.

00:25:47.190 --> 00:25:48.070 align:middle line:90%
