are Benches of Dreams.

00:25:51.730 --> 00:25:54.340 align:middle line:84%
>> They are beginning
to spread, yes.

00:25:54.340 --> 00:25:56.000 align:middle line:90%
>> How did the idea come about?

00:25:56.000 --> 00:25:58.510 align:middle line:84%
Do you sit here and
