00:25:58.510 --> 00:25:59.320 align:middle line:90%
>> Well, here.

00:25:59.320 --> 00:26:02.080 align:middle line:84%
But also-- and
mostly in Costa Rica,

00:26:02.080 --> 00:26:06.640 align:middle line:84%
because we're located on a
sacred mountain, the legend

00:26:06.640 --> 00:26:12.160 align:middle line:84%
