will be come true

00:26:16.150 --> 00:26:18.617 align:middle line:90%
when you dreamed on sacred Mt.

00:26:18.617 --> 00:26:19.780 align:middle line:90%
Rasur.

00:26:19.780 --> 00:26:21.130 align:middle line:90%
>> Or on these benches.

