last, because the
religions have decided

00:33:26.190 --> 00:33:31.110 align:middle line:84%
to work together around the
concept of global spirituality.

00:33:31.110 --> 00:33:35.880 align:middle line:84%
Years ago, one of my first
books was called "New Genesis.

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:38.650 align:middle line:84%
The Birth of a
Global Spirituality."

00:33:38.650 --> 00:33:42.450 align:middle line:84%
So that all the religions
would get together.

00:33:42.450 --> 00:33:45.120 align:middle line:84%
And I made a speech in the
World Parliament of Religions

00:33:45.120 --> 00:33:46.580 align:middle line:90%
in 1990.

00:33:46.580 --> 00:33:50.750 align:middle line:84%
So I said, for heaven's sake,
create a united religions

00:33:50.750 --> 00:33:53.130 align:middle line:90%
like the United Nations.

00:33:53.130 --> 00:33:55.360 align:middle line:84%
And Bishop Desmond Tutu,
the Nobel Prize winner,

00:33:55.360 --> 00:33:56.160 align:middle line:90%
listened to me.

00:33:56.160 --> 00:33:58.230 align:middle line:84%
And I said, then
don't wait another 100

00:33:58.230 --> 00:34:01.050 align:middle line:84%
years to have the next
Parliament of Religions.

00:34:01.050 --> 00:34:03.700 align:middle line:84%
And he convened it
in South Africa.

00:34:03.700 --> 00:34:05.340 align:middle line:84%
So that the Parliament
of Religions

00:34:05.340 --> 00:34:08.055 align:middle line:84%
can become the General
Assembly of the Religious.

00:34:08.055 --> 00:34:09.179 align:middle line:90%
And now they work together.

