00:35:25.170 --> 00:35:30.900 align:middle line:84%
If you are very
unhappy, even the body

00:35:30.900 --> 00:35:34.340 align:middle line:90%
sags to a certain point.

00:35:34.340 --> 00:35:38.790 align:middle line:84%
So that smiles and
the face speaks.

00:35:38.790 --> 00:35:42.480 align:middle line:84%
And I'm always
impressed by a man

00:35:42.480 --> 00:35:45.910 align:middle line:84%
who was the president of
Costa Rica, Rodrigo Carazo,

00:35:45.910 --> 00:35:47.610 align:middle line:84%
and who came to
the United Nations

00:35:47.610 --> 00:35:50.700 align:middle line:84%
to propose the creation of
